# Physics Classroom - Core Architecture

## Technology Stack

- **Framework**: Next.js 15 with App Router + React 19 + TypeScript
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui + Radix UI primitives
- **Database**: Supabase (PostgreSQL) with real-time features
- **Authentication**: NextAuth.js v5 with Supabase adapter
- **AI Integration**: OpenAI API for question generation and grading
- **Math Rendering**: KaTeX for mathematical expressions

## Critical File Locations

- **Types**: [src/types/assignment.ts](mdc:src/types/assignment.ts), [src/types/question-bank.ts](mdc:src/types/question-bank.ts), [src/types/assignment-system.ts](mdc:src/types/assignment-system.ts)
- **Contexts**: [src/contexts/AssignmentContext.tsx](mdc:src/contexts/AssignmentContext.tsx), [src/contexts/QuestionBankContext.tsx](mdc:src/contexts/QuestionBankContext.tsx), [src/contexts/VocabularyContext.tsx](mdc:src/contexts/VocabularyContext.tsx)
- **Auth Config**: [src/lib/auth.ts](mdc:src/lib/auth.ts), [src/lib/permissions.ts](mdc:src/lib/permissions.ts)
- **Database Client**: [src/lib/supabase.ts](mdc:src/lib/supabase.ts)
- **Physics Curriculum**: [src/data/physics-units.ts](mdc:src/data/physics-units.ts)

## Provider Hierarchy

The app uses nested providers in [src/app/layout.tsx](mdc:src/app/layout.tsx):

```
AuthProvider (NextAuth)
└── ToastProvider (Notifications)
    └── QuestionBankProvider (Question management)
        └── AssignmentProvider (Assignment management)
            └── VocabularyProvider (Vocabulary games)
```

## Import Organization Rule

ALWAYS organize imports in this exact order:
```typescript
// 1. React/Next.js imports
import { useEffect, useState } from 'react'
import { NextRequest, NextResponse } from 'next/server'

// 2. External package imports
import { useSession } from 'next-auth/react'

// 3. Internal imports with @/ prefix
import { Button } from '@/components/ui/button'
import { useAssignments } from '@/contexts/AssignmentContext'
```

## Environment Variables

Required in `.env.local`:
```
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=your_supabase_url
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your_supabase_key
NEXTAUTH_SECRET=your_nextauth_secret
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_key
```